categories: Category:Battles of the uprising against the First Order

nodes.text: In 35 ABY, in the aftermath of the Battle of Exegol and the death of Darth Sidious, an uprising against the First Order took place on the planet of Jakku, as the destruction of Sidious' forces at the hands of the Resistance had inspired the inhabitants of the galaxy to rise up. During the uprising, a Resurgent-class Star Destroyer was destroyed and crashed near the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Inflictor in the Starship Graveyard.
